c: 33
v: 55
t: "Akuyi kuba sisono kuwo (amakhosikazi oMprofeti) ukuba avela engazigqumanga phambi kooyise bawo, okanye oonyana bawo, okanye kubanakwawo, okanye koonyana babanakwawo, okanye oonyana boodade wabo okanye kubafazi bawo abakholwayo, okanye kumakhobokazana wawo kananjalo nina yoyikani uAllâh inene uAllâh UliNgqina ngaphezulu kwezinto zonke"